|}
</center>

上面的表格说明，在四配位化合物中离去配体比五配位化合物中需要更高的能量。总的来说，硅化合物中离去配体所需能量比磷化合物低，这是因为硅化合物中的键较弱。

总之，电荷密度改变在计算超配位的硅化合物和磷化合物的反应活性增大时是无意义的。此外，更弱的键造成了反应活性的增加，特别是磷化合物的轴向位置<ref name=abinitio1/>。

=== 应用 ===
这一机理的影响扩展到六配位的硅化合物，这被认为是使用烯丙基三氟硅烷进行醛的[[烯丙基化反应|烯丙基化反应]]的过渡态。该反应只在氟离子活化六配位过渡态之前进行，并削弱了六配位过渡态中硅和碳之间的化学键，促使该反应进行<ref name=abinitio3>{{en}}{{cite journal | title = Regiospecific and highly stereoselective allylation of aldehydes with allyltrifluorosilane activated by fluoride ions. | journal = [[四面体通讯|Tetrahedron Letters]] | year = 1987 | volume = 28 | pages = 4081–4084 | doi = 10.1016/S0040-4039(01)83867-3 | author1 = Kira, M | author2 = Kobayashi, M. | author3 = Sakurai, H.}}</ref>。

[[File:Aldehyde_crotylation_with_hypervalent_silicon.png|thumb]]

== 第二周期超价分子 ==
这类化合物是很罕见的，稳定性也较差由于[[第2周期元素|第2周期元素]]没有价层d轨道，这使得用[[混成軌域|杂化轨道理论]]无法解释它们的成键。但正是它们的不稳定性也说明了d轨道参与成键虽少，但也会使体系的能量下降<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal|coauthors=Schleyer, Paul v. R.|title=Chemical bonding in hypervalent molecules. The dominance of ionic bonding and negative hyperconjugation over d-orbital participation|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|date=1990-02-01|volume=112|issue=4|pages=1434–1445|doi=10.1021/ja00160a022|last=Reed|first=Alan E.}}</ref>。

=== 硼 ===
硼的五配位化合物也已被合成出来。一个例子中硼与两个[[嘧啶|嘧啶]]环上的[[电子雲|电子-{}-雲]]密度较高的氮原子形成N-B-N[[三中心四电子键|三中心四电子键]]<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal|coauthors=Kojima, Satoshi, Yamamoto, Yohsuke|title=A Hypervalent Pentacoordinate Boron Compound with an N−B−N Three-Center Four-Electron Bond|journal=The Journal of Organic Chemistry|date=2011-04-01|volume=76|issue=7|pages=2123–2131|doi=10.1021/jo1024656|last=Hirano|first=Yuichi}}</ref>。甚至六配位的化合物也有报道<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal|coauthors=Martin, J. C.|title=Compounds of pentacoordinate (10-B-5) and hexacoordinate (12-B-6) hypervalent boron|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|date=1984-09-01|volume=106|issue=19|pages=5745–5746|doi=10.1021/ja00331a064|last=Lee|first=David Y.}}</ref>。

=== 碳 ===
{{main|碳鎓离子}}
[[File:Methonium.svg|thumb]]
甲鎓离子（CH<sub>5</sub><sup>+</sup>）等[[碳鎓离子|碳鎓离子]]是五配位碳化合物的典型例子，可以认为其中含有一个[[三中心两电子键|三中心二电子键]]<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal|coauthors=Klopman, Gilles; Schlosberg, Richard H.|title=Super acids. III. Protonation of alkanes and intermediacy of alkanonium ions, pentacoordinated carbon cations of CH5+ type. Hydrogen exchange, protolytic cleavage, hydrogen abstraction; polycondensation of methane, ethane, 2,2-dimethylpropane and 2,2,3,3-tetramethylbutane in FSO3H-SbF5|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|date=1969-06-01|volume=91|issue=12|pages=3261–3268|doi=10.1021/ja01040a029|last=Olah|first=George A.}}</ref>。但其中的氢能不断地发生交换反应，甚至[[绝对零度|绝对零度]]下也能发生。这使得甲鎓离子成为一种[[流变分子|流变分子]]，[[核磁共振|核磁共振氢谱]]上始终只有一个峰<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal | title = CH<sub>5</sub><sup>+</sup>: The Infrared Spectrum Observed | author = Edmund T. White, Jian Tang, Takeshi Oka | journal = [[科学_(期刊)|Science]] | volume = 284 | pages = 135 | year = 1999 | doi = 10.1126/science.284.5411.135}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite journal | title = Understanding the Infrared Spectrum of Bare CH5+ | author = Oskar Asvany, Padma Kumar P, Britta Redlich, Ilka Hegemann, Stephan Schlemmer, Dominik Marx | journal = [[科学_(期刊)|Science]] | volume = 309 | pages = 1219–22 | year = 2005 | doi = 10.1126/science.1113729 | pmid = 15994376 | issue = 5738}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite journal | title = Quantum Deconstruction of the Infrared Spectrum of CH5+ | author = Xinchuan Huang, Anne B. McCoy, [[Joel_Bowman|Joel M. Bowman]], Lindsay M. Johnson, Chandra Savage, Feng Dong, David J. Nesbitt | journal = [[科学_(期刊)|Science]] | year = 2006 | volume = 311 | issue = 5757 | pages = 60–63 | doi = 10.1126/science.1121166 | pmid = 16400143}}</ref>。由于锂的原子半径与氢较接近，还存在CLi<sub>5</sub><sup>+</sup>离子<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal|coauthors=Chandrasekhar, Jayaraman; Wuerthwein, Ernst Ulrich; Schleyer, Paul von Rague; Chinn, John W.; Landro, Frederick J.; Lagow, Richard J.; Luke, Brian; Pople, John A.|title=Lithiated carbocations. The generation, structure, and stability of CLi5+|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|date=1982-07-01|volume=104|issue=15|pages=4275–4276|doi=10.1021/ja00379a051|last=Jemmis|first=Eluvathingal D.}}</ref>。

[[双分子亲核取代反应|双分子亲核取代反应]]（S<sub>N</sub>2）的过渡态是一个超价阴离子。一些特殊的阴离子理论上可以较稳定存在，例如[At—C(CN)<sub>3</sub>—At]<sup>-</sup>和[Ng—CR<sub>3</sub>—Ng]<sup>-</sup>（Ng代表[[稀有气体|稀有气体]]原子），它们的空间构型都是三角双锥<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal|coauthors=van Stralen, Sebastiaan J. M., van Stralen, Joost N. P., Fonseca Guerra, Célia, Bickelhaupt, F. Matthias|title=Hypervalent Carbon Atom: “Freezing” the S<sub>N</sub>2 Transition State|journal=Angewandte Chemie International Edition|date=2009-08-16|volume=48|issue=35|pages=6469–6471|doi=10.1002/anie.200902125|last=Pierrefixe|first=Simon C. A. H.}}</ref>。

此外，碳与锂形成的化合物CLi<sub>5</sub>和CLi<sub>6</sub>相对稳定，它们分解成CLi<sub>4</sub>和Li<sub>2</sub>的过程是吸热的<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal|title=Observation of hypervalent CLi6 by Knudsen-effusion mass spectrometry|journal=Nature|date=1992-01-29|volume=355|issue=6359|pages=432–434|doi=10.1038/355432a0|last=Kudo|first=Hiroshi}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite journal|coauthors=Wuerthwein, Ernst Ulrich; Kaufmann, Elmar; Clark, Timothy; Pople, John A.|title=Effectively hypervalent molecules. 2. Lithium carbide (CLi5), lithium carbide (CLi6), and the related effectively hypervalent first row molecules, CLi5-nHn and CLi6-nHn|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|date=1983-09-01|volume=105|issue=18|pages=5930–5932|doi=10.1021/ja00356a045|last=Schleyer|first=Paul v. R.}}</ref>，其他碱金属的类似化合物也有一定稳定性，但不如锂的这类化合物稳定<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal|coauthors=Boldyrev, A.I.|title=DVM Xα calculations on the electronic structure of “superalkali” cations|journal=Chemical Physics Letters|date=1982-10-01|volume=92|issue=3|pages=262–266|doi=10.1016/0009-2614(82)80272-8|last=Gutsev|first=G.L.}}</ref>。

碳的超价化合物还不止这些，例如{[(Ph<sub>3</sub>PAu)<sub>6</sub>C]<sub>2</sub>}<sup>+</sup><ref>{{en}}{{cite journal|coauthors=Grohmann, Andreas; Huber, Brigitte; Krüger, Carl; Schmidbaur, Hubert|title=“Aurophilicity” as a Consequence of Relativistic Effects: The Hexakis(triphenylphosphaneaurio)methane Dication[(Ph3PAu)6C]2⊕|journal=Angewandte Chemie International Edition in English|date=1988-11-01|volume=27|issue=11|pages=1544–1546|doi=10.1002/anie.198815441|last=Scherbaum|first=Franz}}</ref>、[(Ph<sub>3</sub>PAu)<sub>5</sub>C]<sup>+</sup><ref>{{en}}{{cite journal|coauthors=Grohmann, Andreas; Müller, Gerhard; Schmidbaur, Hubert|title=Synthesis, Structure, and Bonding of the Cation [{(C6H5)3PAu}5C]?|journal=Angewandte Chemie International Edition in English|date=1989-04-01|volume=28|issue=4|pages=463–465|doi=10.1002/anie.198904631|last=Scherbaum|first=Franz}}</ref>和一些更加复杂金[[原子簇|原子簇]]化合物<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal|coauthors=Huber, Brigitte; Müller, Gerhard; Schmidbaur, Hubert|title=Use of the CH Acidity of 2,4,4-Trimethyl-4,5-dihydrooxazole to Synthesize Triauriomethanes and Novel Gold Clusters|journal=Angewandte Chemie International Edition in English|date=1988-11-01|volume=27|issue=11|pages=1542–1544|doi=10.1002/anie.198815421|last=Scherbaum|first=Franz}}</ref>。

=== 氮 ===
{{main|五氟化氮|氨}}
[[File:Nitrogen_pentafluoride_possible_structures.jpg|thumb]]
从前，科学家认为五氟化氮分子是不可能存在的，离子型的NF<sub>4</sub><sup>+</sup>F<sup>-</sup>也是不稳定的<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal|coauthors=Riede, J.; Schmidbaur, H.|title=Electron-deficient bonding at pentacoordinate nitrogen|journal=Nature|date=1990-05-09|volume=345|issue=6271|pages=140–142|doi=10.1038/345140a0|last=Grohmann|first=A.}}</ref>。然而，理论计算表明，三角双锥型的五氟化氮是[[三氟化氮|三氟化氮]]与氟分子结合过程中能量最低的状态。根据[[分子轨道理论|分子轨道理论]]，10个电子分别填充在3个强成键轨道（水平方向的键）、1个弱成键轨道（轴向）、1个非键轨道（轴向）中<ref>{{en}}{{cite book|title=Modeling marvels : computational anticipation of novel molecules|year=2008|publisher=Springer|location=[Dordrecht]|isbn=978-1-4020-6972-7|url=http://books.google.com.hk/books?id=IoFzgBSSCwEC&printsec=frontcover&hl=zh-CN#v=onepage&q&f=false|last=Lewars|first=Errol G.|edition=1. Ed.}}</ref>。使用[[玻恩－哈伯循环|玻恩-哈伯循环]]计算表明，NF<sub>5</sub>与NF<sub>4</sub>F能量仅相差1.0 kJ/mol，都有可能存在。理论上甚至NF<sub>6</sub><sup>-</sup>也是稳定的<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal|coauthors=Wilson, William W.|title=Nitrogen pentafluoride: covalent NF<sub>5</sub> versus ionic NF<sub>4</sub><sup>+</sup>F<sup>-</sup> and studies on the instability of the latter|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|date=1992-11-30|volume=114|issue=25|pages=9934–9936|doi=10.1021/ja00051a027|last=Christe|first=Karl O.}}</ref>。

此外，氨还能与铵根离子形成超价聚合物，化学式可表示为NH<sub>4</sub>(NH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>n</sub>（n=1-3）。这类聚合物可由金属钾对[NH<sub>4</sub>(NH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>n</sub>]<sup>+</sup>的单电子还原制得<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal|coauthors=Porter, Richard F.|title=An experimental study of hypervalent molecular clusters by neutralized ion beam spectroscopy: ammonium-ammonia (NH4(NH3)n) and deuterated ammonium-ammonia (ND4(ND3)n)|journal=The Journal of Physical Chemistry|date=1984-12-01|volume=88|issue=26|pages=6680–6684|doi=10.1021/j150670a035|last=Gellene|first=Gregory I.}}</ref>。

=== 氟 ===
{{main|三氟阴离子}}
由于氟的[[电负性|电负性]]是除暂无化合物的[[稀有气体|稀有气体元素]]氦、氖外最高的，一般不能形成超价分子。但氟也能在超低温下形成不太稳定的F<sub>3</sub><sup>-</sup>离子，因为F<sup>-</sup>与F<sub>2</sub>的结合释放出11 kcal/mol的能量<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal|coauthors=Dykstra, Clifford E.; Martin, J. C.|title=The structure and stability of the 10-F-2 trifluoride ion, a compound of a hypervalent first row element|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|date=1985-10-01|volume=107|issue=22|pages=6359–6362|doi=10.1021/ja00308a032|last=Cahill|first=Paul A.}}</ref>。

